Next in order succeeds the Apostles Creed;

 or summary of our Chrian Faith, to be rehearsed joyntly both by Priest, and all the People standing: Our standing up, with the rest of the Congregation, to signifie and delare, that you will stand to this Faith, and earnestly contend for it as being the same which was once given to or by

 the Saints, the holy Apostles.
